data.description: Truly stunning in sought after Riverwalk! This gorgeous, impeccably maintained home with attached 2 car garage lives large! Excellent location a few hundred feet from shops, restaurants, trails, and access to the Catawba River! Homes on this premier street in the neighborhood rarely come on the market. Light, bright and en trend finishes throughout. The expansive kitchen has been elegantly updated with Miami Vena quartz countertops, herringbone marble backsplash & a beautiful stainless steel gas range, microwave and refrigerator. Flooring on the second level has been updated with luxury vinyl plank - no carpets! Enjoy our Carolina evenings on the covered balcony off the primary bedroom! Wonderful built-ins & storage space! Other extras include a closet system, recently painted exterior doors & decking, and even an infrared air purifier system! Don't miss this fantastic home and elevated lifestyle!
